data.description: Excellently cared for and maintained inside and out! This home features hardwood floors in the foyer, dining room, great room and a downstairs primary bedroom with a trey ceiling and newly renovated primary bath. Great room has a vaulted ceiling and a natural gas log fireplace. Kitchen is open to the great room with a breakfast area! There are two bedrooms upstairs along with a bonus room! There is a 16x27-foot deck overlooking a large yard with a storage shed. Also includes a double-car garage.
